8998 rated r 
 
throw momma from the train could have been titled how to 
kill your mother and cure writers block 
a hopelessly bad writer with a hellion of a mother meets a 
college professor who cant get past the first three words of a 
book hes trying to write and despises his far more successful 
former wife 
inspired by alfred hitchcocks strangers on a train the 
aspiring writer proposes a hitchcockian double murder and ensnares 
